title: Snoop Dogg | Do My Thang

Shop the Neff x Snoop Collection:
Neff Headwear teamed up with Snoop Dogg for the video to his new single "Do My Thang" off the "7 Days of Funk" album with Snoop and Dam Funk. The video features several items from the new Neff x Snoop Collection available exclusively at Tilly's.
